{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 1, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:00:13.674290+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨雾尚未散尽，村中央的许愿井泛着微光。你站在草垛旁，村长艾琳快步朝你走来，眼中满是忧虑与期待。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "啊，你终于醒了！我是晨露村的村长艾琳。最近恶龙肆虐，掳走了好几个孩子……村民们都说，你是被神选中的勇者。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家初次与村长艾琳对话，艾琳确认玩家身份为被选中的勇者，并提及恶龙掳走孩童的危机。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_001:-:-:1b772e90", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:6058d881"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 3, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 19}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 2, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:00:32.958958+00:00", "player_text": "我该干什么", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "艾琳站在许愿井旁，双手紧握围裙边缘，神情既期待又不安。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "年轻人，你既然醒了，就该行动起来了。最近哥布林在幽影森林异常活跃，甚至有村民在那里失踪……我听说精灵守卫瑟琳正在调查此事。或许你可以先去森林看看？"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [{"quest_id": "quest_side_001", "title": null, "category": null, "status": null, "objective": null, "guidance": "前往幽影森林（loc_002），寻找精灵守卫瑟琳并收集月光苔与夜露花。", "giver_npc_id": null, "reward_hint": null, "required_items": {}, "reward_items": {}, "collected_items_delta": {}}], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家询问下一步行动，村长艾琳建议前往幽影森林调查哥布林异常活动，并提及精灵守卫瑟琳。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_001:-:-:1b772e90", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:6058d881", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:1:-:8e2d525d"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 5, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 20}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 3, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:00:55.891490+00:00", "player_text": "当然可以", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨雾渐渐散去，阳光洒在许愿井的石沿上。艾琳松开紧握的围裙，神情略显放松，但仍带着一丝忧虑。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "太好了，你愿意帮忙！幽影森林就在村子东边，不过要小心——最近不止有哥布林出没，还有人说看见了黑影在树丛中游荡。记得去找瑟琳，她应该在森林入口附近守着。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家表示愿意行动，村长艾琳确认其前往幽影森林的计划，并提醒注意安全，同时指引寻找精灵守卫瑟琳。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_001:-:-:1b772e90", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:6058d881", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:-:be0a5773", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:1:-:8e2d525d", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:2:-:1a7100c6"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 7, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 21}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 4, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:01:17.931344+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_005", "location_id": "loc_002", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "幽影森林深处，树影婆娑，光线稀薄。你站在一处古老石碑旁，前方站着一位身披翠绿斗篷的精灵守卫，目光如刃。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_005", "text": "凡人，此地非你久留之所。速速离去。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_002", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家初次抵达幽影森林，遇见精灵守卫瑟琳。瑟琳以高傲冷漠的态度警告玩家离开。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_002:-:-:7edfec3f", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_005:-:-:-:b583f660", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:1:-:8e2d525d", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:2:-:1a7100c6", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:3:-:2f4ff589"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:-:07ee89c2", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:-:be0a5773"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_005", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_002", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 6, "retrieved": 3, "store_total": 22}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 5, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:01:56.449049+00:00", "player_text": "你最近是不是在调查什么", "npc_id": "npc_005", "location_id": "loc_002", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "幽影森林中，微风拂过古老石碑，瑟琳的翠绿斗篷轻轻摆动。她目光如刃，语气依旧冷峻，但略带一丝审视。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_005", "text": "凡人，你倒是有几分敏锐。我确实在调查哥布林的异动——它们竟敢亵渎精灵遗迹。若你真有心助我，就去采集月光苔与夜露花。没有这些，森林的邪气无法净化。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [{"quest_id": "quest_side_001", "title": "森林的低语", "category": "side", "status": "active", "objective": "收集月光苔×2、夜露花×1，交给瑟琳。", "guidance": "在幽影森林中寻找月光苔和夜露花。", "giver_npc_id": "npc_005", "reward_hint": "完成任务后将获得精灵之弓。", "required_items": {"月光苔": 2, "夜露花": 1}, "reward_items": {"精灵之弓": 1}, "collected_items_delta": {}}], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家询问瑟琳是否在调查什么，瑟琳承认正在调查哥布林对精灵遗迹的亵渎，并要求玩家协助采集月光苔与夜露花以净化森林邪气。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_002:-:-:7edfec3f", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_005:-:-:-:b583f660", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:4:-:8b85dd94", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:2:-:1a7100c6", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:3:-:2f4ff589", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:4:-:f8ae3381"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:-:be0a5773", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:-:07ee89c2", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filter