{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 8, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:03:15.600281+00:00", "player_text": "我帮完精灵了，我现在该干什么", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨露村的许愿井旁，阳光洒在青石板上。艾琳正望着村口方向，见你归来，眼中闪过一丝欣慰。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "你回来了！听说你帮瑟琳净化了森林的邪气，真是了不起。不过，勇者的使命才刚刚开始——恶龙仍在肆虐，我们还需要水之圣杯和火焰之心。或许你可以去月光湖找水之祭司诺亚，或者去铁砧镇拜访铁匠巴洛克，他们或许能指引你下一步该做什么。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家告知已协助精灵完成任务，村长艾琳肯定其贡献，并建议前往月光湖或铁砧镇继续寻找水之圣杯与火焰之心的线索。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_001:-:-:1b772e90", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:6058d881", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:-:be0a5773", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:-:07ee89c2", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:5:-:719becae", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:6:-:d2c11834", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:7:-:dd3fff4f"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:7:-:c92ca7cc", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:5:-:12347984"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lo