{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 9, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:03:46.886367+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_008", "location_id": "loc_004", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "月光湖面如镜，微风拂过，泛起银色涟漪。你站在湖畔，水之祭司诺亚静立于浅水中，长袍随波轻荡，目光深邃如湖底。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_008", "text": "旅人，湖水已感知你的到来。我是诺亚，守护此地的水之祭司。你携带着精灵之弓……看来幽影森林的低语已平息。但湖底的圣杯仍沉睡，邪灵的阴影正悄然逼近。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_004", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家初次抵达月光湖，与水之祭司诺亚对话。诺亚确认玩家已完成森林任务，并暗示湖底圣杯任务尚未开始。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_004:-:-:b06384c9", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_008:-:-:-:9b3f974a", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:6:-:d2c11834", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:7:-:dd3fff4f", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:8:-:209af24e"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:7:-:c92ca7cc", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:4:-:8b85dd94", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:6:-:c041304b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:5:-:12347984"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_008", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_