{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 13, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:05:29.462453+00:00", "player_text": "我去完月光湖了", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨露村的许愿井旁，阳光洒在青石板上。艾琳正低头整理手中的草药，听见你的脚步声后抬起头，眼中满是关切。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "你从月光湖回来了？太好了！我听说水之祭司诺亚已经把水之圣杯交给你了——这可是对抗恶龙的关键之物啊。现在，你手上已经有了精灵之弓和水之圣杯，就差火焰之心了。铁匠巴洛克在铁砧镇等你，他或许能帮你完成最后一件圣物的收集。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家告知已从月光湖返回，村长艾琳确认其已获得水之圣杯，并指引其前往铁砧镇寻找铁匠巴洛克以获取火焰之心。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_001:-:-:1b772e90", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:6058d881", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:-:be0a5773", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:-:07ee89c2", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:8:-:3e535b62", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:10:-:9f4fd08a", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:11:-:0b7d6324", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:12:-:9fd4efa0"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_008:loc_004:12:-:bfb4500e"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary