{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 14, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:09:46.759314+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_006", "location_id": "loc_003", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "铁砧镇的熔炉熊熊燃烧，火星四溅。你站在铁匠铺前，巴洛克正抡起大锤敲打一块通红的铁坯。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_006", "text": "哟！勇者来了？听说你已经拿到了精灵之弓和水之圣杯，不错嘛！不过想从我这儿拿到火焰之心？哼！没材料就别来烦我！等你找到黑曜石、火蜥蜴鳞片和火山灰再说！"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_003", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家初次抵达铁砧镇，与铁匠巴洛克对话。巴洛克确认玩家已有两件圣物，但要求其先收集黑曜石×2、火蜥蜴鳞片×3、火山灰×1才能打造火焰之心。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_003:-:-:55c9248f", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_006:-:-:-:935f62e5", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:11:-:0b7d6324", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:12:-:9fd4efa0", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:13:-:19ad54a8"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:13:-:f3796658", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:4:-:8b85dd94", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:7:-:c92ca7cc", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_005:loc_002:6:-:c041304b"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_135750_30118ad4", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "npc_id": "npc_006", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "location_id": "loc_003", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "