{"session_id": "20260315_135750_30118ad4", "turn_index": 18, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T14:11:09.037834+00:00", "player_text": "我去完铁毡镇回来了", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨露村的许愿井旁，阳光洒在青石板上。艾琳放下手中的草药，快步迎向你，眼中闪烁着激动与希望。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "你从铁砧镇回来了？太好了！我刚刚听说巴洛克已经把火焰之心交给你了——现在你集齐了三件圣物：精灵之弓、水之圣杯和火焰之心！勇者啊，是时候前往龙之巢了。恶龙就在黑石山深处的巢穴里，只有你能终结这场灾难。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [{"quest_id": "quest_main_001", "title": null, "category": null, "status": "active", "objective": null, "guidance": "前往龙之巢（loc_006），使用三件圣物击败恶龙。", "giver_npc_id": null, "reward_hint": null, "required_items": {}, "reward_items": {}, "collected_items_delta": {}}], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家告知已从铁砧镇返回，村长艾琳确认其已获得火焰之心，并宣布三件圣物已齐备，指引其前往龙之巢挑战恶龙。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_135750_30118ad4:world_bible:-:-:-:-:0807772b", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:location:-:loc_001:-:-:1b772e90", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:6058d881", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:c6596328", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:-:be0a5773", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:-:07ee89c2", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:8:-:3e535b62", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:memory:npc_001:loc_001:13:-:f3796658", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:15:-:b9ae0d28", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:16:-:a173113d", "20260315_135750_30118ad4:summary:-:-:17:-:a7df3545"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstor